para_trans: To meet the expenditure on service charges, GST and other ancillary matters in addition to the remuneration / salary of the manpower paid by external agencies in PRM Vatsalya, Pa Shakti and other such Centrally Sponsored Schemes.
Regarding the approval of the accounting exam.
Department of Women and Child Development
Madam Cama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Reference: - Date of the meeting of the High Level Committee. 09.04.2025 Government Decisions: -

The Government is approving the following new heads of accounts to meet the expenditure on service charges, GST and other ancillary matters in addition to the remuneration / salary of the manpower paid through external agencies in the "Mission Vatsalya," "Far Shakti" and other similar Centrally Sponsored Schemes implemented by the Department of Women and Child Development.
The decision was taken with the concurrence of the Planning and Finance Department and the Accountant General, Mumbai.
This Government decision is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
